Package org.mcennis.graphrat.algorithm.reusablecores.distance

Interface Summary
DistanceFunction Interface abstracting distance functions.
 

Class Summary
ChebyshevDistance Distance measure as defined in Wikipedia
CosineDistance Adapted from Anna Huang's distance metric for Weka by Daniel McEnnis
DistanceFactory Class for creating a distance function.
DotProductDistance distance measure of dot-product of the two vectors as vectors in a Euclidean space.
EuclideanDistance Euclidean distance measure as defined in Wikipedia
JaccardDistance Jaccard Distance function adapted from Anna Huang's Weka Distance function by Daniel McEnnis
ManhattanDistance Manhattan Distance measure as defined in Wikipedia
PearsonDistance Adapted from Anna Huang's Pearson distance metric for Weka by Daniel McEnnis
WeightedKLDDistance Weighted KLDistance function Adapted from Anna Huang's Weka implementation.
